  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222530/extras/0c113ad211000a6f15c4efc1d9e36354.avif?t=1733857134\" width=650 height=200 /></span><br>A game where you are chased by a motorcycle. Based on a true story (only the park like map)<br>In this game, you need to collect five photos before you can escape the current map. Simple.<br>But be careful! One wrong step and you can end up drowing in the water with no help nearby, or get stuck in traps. And if you don't get unstuck quickly, she will find you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222530/extras/cf4731f9a4fc53b4846750e8abd5c8d5.poster.avif?t=1733857134\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222530/extras/cf4731f9a4fc53b4846750e8abd5c8d5.webm?t=1733857134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222530/extras/cf4731f9a4fc53b4846750e8abd5c8d5.mp4?t=1733857134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222530/extras/984522e443309c4fee480dfe9fd30b65.avif?t=1733857134\" width=650 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story Mode</li><li>Challenge Mode (speedrun mode)</li><li>Integrated autosplitter vars for all my speedrunners out there (more about that on the game website)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222530/extras/0c113ad211000a6f15c4efc1d9e36354.avif?t=1733857134\" width=650 height=200 /></span><br>A game where you are chased by a motorcycle. Based on a true story (only the park like map)<br>In this game, you need to collect five photos before you can escape the current map. Simple.<br>But be careful! One wrong step and you can end up drowing in the water with no help nearby, or get stuck in traps. And if you don't get unstuck quickly, she will find you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222530/extras/cf4731f9a4fc53b4846750e8abd5c8d5.poster.avif?t=1733857134\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222530/extras/cf4731f9a4fc53b4846750e8abd5c8d5.webm?t=1733857134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222530/extras/cf4731f9a4fc53b4846750e8abd5c8d5.mp4?t=1733857134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222530/extras/984522e443309c4fee480dfe9fd30b65.avif?t=1733857134\" width=650 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story Mode</li><li>Challenge Mode (speedrun mode)</li><li>Integrated autosplitter vars for all my speedrunners out there (more about that on the game website)</li></ul>",
